{
  "stem": "22892.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I got out of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And here was like a battle zone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You see wounded soldiers and-- on sleds, on-- in-- and dogs pulling them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You could see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I mean, you could see-- yeah, I don't know if you're familiar with Katyusha rockets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "At that time, the, the Russians, that was like their secret weapon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I saw these Katyusha rockets firing on the other side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Well, I was the only kid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I mean, it's all soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There's no civilians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You don't see anybody on the-- on, on, on the outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Well, there's a Russian army trucks going back and forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I hitchhiked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It's-- it, it, it was pointing to Rowne, which was further east.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And guy stopped the truck and let me get in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And it was just the truck driver and I driving.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I think he, he also needed me for a reason.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I think the choke was-- he had to hold onto the choke for him to drive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was an old truck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And, and it was-- I remember, he gave me a-- it was a piece of wood and-- to hold it on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Because this way, it relieves his-- you know, he could do the driving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got to Rowne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rowne was further east.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only about 60 kilometers, 40, 50 miles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I end up in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's when I ran into one of my cousins who survived, Uncle Meir's son.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was about two or-- about three years older than I was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And was I happy to see him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was-- while the war was going on, he wanted to, to go into the army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wanted to volunteer in the Russian army, so he could take revenge, kill Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
